name: ANOTHER DAY IN PARADISE
description:
Fabulous bib necklace handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids shades of green, orange, yellow, pink and purple.

Also used in these earrings are opaque glass beads in yellow, turquoise nad orange, hexagonal TOHO beads in dark green and purple, silver lined beads in orange and green, neon green round beads, hot pink TOHO beads. The stones used are: two little Swarovski crystal Rose Montees Volcano stones, neon green baguettes, fuchsia rectangular stones, oval turquoise stones, hot pink oval centre stone, neon yellow glass rectangular stones, blue lagoon glass pear stones, neon yellow glass pear stones, oval orange stones and neon pink glass pear stones. 

Necklace backed with natural leather. On 12K gold coloured link chain closing with a lobster claw.

name: KRYPTONITE
description:
Beautiful small earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in navy, light taupe and raspberry.

Also used in these earrings are frosted lime TOHO beads, shiny glass brown beads, TOHO Delica beads in dark rose and lavender, opaque navy hexagonal beads, Oxblood cube beads, champagne half coated rondelle beads, Swarovski crystal Rose Montees Volcano stones, neon glass faceted pear shaped stone and metalic glass faceted pear drop. 

Backed with natural leather. On ear wires.

These are approx. 7 cm long and 3 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 2,75" long by 1,18" wide

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.

name: FROST YOURSELF
description:
Lovely earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in cream and light silver

Also used in these earrings are light grey and white opal TOHO beads, Swarovski square white opal stones and glass crystal navette stones.

Backed with natural leather. On ear posts.

These are approx. 5 cm long and 4 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 1,96" long by 1,57" wide

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.

name: SYRINGA VULGARIS
description:
Pretty earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in lilac.

Also used in these earrings are cyclamen opal round beads, purple tube beads, rainbow purple cube beads, lilac faceted oval beads, amethyst round Swarovski stone, glass crystal navettes, round rivolli in lilac, Swarovski triangles in Tanzanite and vintage glass pear drops in opaque lilac.


Backed with natural leather. On ear posts.

These are approx. 5,5 cm long and 2,6 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 2,16" long by 0,98" wide

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.

name: PROVENCE FIELDS
description:
Beautiful earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in silver, purple, lavender and lime.

Pastels + neon = hottest trend!

Also used in these earrings are grey glass beads, rainbow lilac cube beads, luster purple cube beads, round lilac opal beads, purple bugle beads, Swarovski Cyclamen opal stones, lavender rivoli stones and rectangular neon lime stones.

Backed with natural leather. On ear wires.

These are approx. 8,5 cm long and 3,5 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 3,34" long by 1,37" wide

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.

name: MINT LEMONADE
description:
Awesome earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in turquoise and lime.

Cool colours for hot summer days :)

I've also used matt cube beads, mint MIYUKI beads, TOHO beads in aqua lime, frosted beads in sour apple, frosted white beads, pear shaped and rectangular neon yellow glass stones.

Backed with natural leather. On ear wires.

These are approx. 7,5 cm long and 3,8 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 2,95" long by 1,49" wide

name: GRAPEFRUIT JULEP
description:
Beautiful earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in cream and coral.

Cool pastels for hot weather!

Also used in these earrings are  celery TOHO beads, frosted clear beads, coral beads, Swarovski beads in pacific opal, glass beads in white opal, rectangular coral stone and square mint stone.

Backed with natural leather. On ear wires.

These are approx. 7.7 cm long and 4 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 3,03" long by 1,57" wide

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.

name: I'M IN HEAVEN
description:
deco bridal soutache earrings with Swarovski elements in rose water opal and pacific opal

Beautiful earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in ivory, pastel green and pastel pink. Shapes on these follow the Deco trend! Beautiful stones are all Swarovski crystals, some are vintage colours.

I've used Japanese beads in rose water, light pink, white opal and frosted rainbow green. Stones are all Swarovski elements including small rounds in pacific opal, rounds in mint alabaster, bigger rounds and oval in pacific opal also round rose water opal stone, round beads in rose water opal and rose alabaster. The rose alabaster tear drops are high quality glass.

Backed with natural leather. On rhodium ear wires.

These are approx. 9 cm long and 4,5 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 3,54" long by 1,77" wide

name: STRAWBERRIES AND CREAM
description:
soutache earrings in pinks with ivory and white opal

Pretty earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in ivory and pale silver. CLovely pastel shades to brighten your styling.


I've also used opaque pink beads, pink rainbow TOHO beads, white opal glass beads, clear pink beads, rose water opal Swarovski beads, white opal faceted glass beads, rose round stones, Swarovski white opal stones and rose alabaster pear shaped stones.

Backed with natural leather. On ear posts

These are approx. 7 cm long and 4 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 2,75" long by 1,57" wide

name: FIGHT FIRE WITH FIRE
description:
soutache earrings in orange, purple and pink with Swarovski crystals

Beautiful earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in orange, pink, purple and taupe.

I've also used seed beads in rainbow, white opal, square rainbow, faceted copper beads, and Swarovski crystals: oval Black Diamond Chili Pepper, round Heliotrope and Light Rose Brandy Pear.

Backed with natural leather. On gunmetal ear wires

These are approx. 8,5 cm long and 3,5 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 3,34" long by 1,37" wide

name: DARK KNIGHT
description:
soutache earrings in black, gunmetal and iris teal

Big opulent earings handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in black and gunmetal.
I've also used metalic gunmetal glass beads, matt gunmetal TOHO beads, matte TOHO beads in iris teal, faceted black picasso beads, faceted shiny black beads and matte iris beads, square TOHO beads in matte black, black acrylic faceted crystals with and without cases. With chain in gunmetal.

Backed with natural leather. Ear posts are sterling silver with soft rubber earring back or ear clips if required. Please message me which you prefer.

These are approx. 9,5 cm long including chain and 4,8 cm wide in the widest place. That is approx. 3,74" long by 1,89" wide

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.

name: SELENE
description:
statement studded bib necklace in turquoise, purple and old gold

Highly unique embroidered statement necklace in turquoise and purple with addition of old gold and grey/silver.

For this necklace I have used round and oval faceted crystals in purple, gray baguettes, turquoise and brass squares, round, square, tear shaped and diamond shaped acrylic stones, brass triangles, silver cubes and gold cuboids, turquoise glass oblong beads, oval turquoise faceted crystals in settings, gunmetal rectangular faceted crystal in setting, pear shaped purple crystal in setting, tiny purple seed beads, turquoise bugle beads and big pyramid stud in old gold.

Backed with natural leather in black. On brass chain fastened with lobster clasp

The embroidered part of the necklece is 25 by 17,5cm . That's 9.84" by 6.88".

name: VERY MULBERRY
description:
soutache statement necklace in burgundy, pink, gray and bronze

Highly unique statement necklace handmade using the soutache embroidery technique with soutache braids in gray, champagne, burgundy, dusky pink and copper.

I've also used round pink and gunmetal TOHO beads, square bronze and brown TOHO beads, faceted bronze beads, round red coral beads, bronze bugle beads, faceted burgundy and gray crystals and light pink faceted crystals in gold settings. 

Backed with natural leather in dark brown. Ties with burgundy grosgrain ribbon.

The embroidered part of the necklece is 15 cm wide by 13 cm high. That's 5.9" wide by 5.11" high.

This is one-off product and will not be repeated in this colourway.
